{"tid":1773208,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"200人參與聲援印傭女作家","createTime":"2019-12-07T09:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T10:03:22.000Z","uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c920a3612d75561432ccfd1762d9cfc22148123","tid":1773208,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"曾在網媒報道反修例運動的印傭Yuli Riswati，早前因忘記續領工作簽證，被入境處遞解出境。Yuli朋友組成的支援組織，下午發起在中環愛丁堡廣場集會，約200人參與聲援，期間有人舉起標語、高叫口號及寫明信片。<br />\n<br />\n大會致電身處印尼的Yuli，她一度咽哽，感謝香港人及朋友的支持，她正在印尼看醫生及服藥。Yuli憶述在青山灣入境事務中心，被扣留兩星期時情緒抑鬱及不時受驚，亦曾突然被人搜身，又指作為伊斯蘭教徒，不希望在男醫生面前脫衣檢查身體。她形容環境比大欖及羅湖監獄更惡劣，希望社會關注其他在港家傭的權益。<br />\n<br />\n支援組成員阿飛說，法庭11月已裁定Yuli無罪，要求入境處交代羈留期限及改善待遇，又引述有家務工擔心，透過社交媒體表達意見會被針對，是否代表不能在港支持民主，促請政府尊重外傭的政治參與及言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n市民潘先生說，聽到Yuli在電話中首先關心香港人，感到非常感動又心痛，批評政府漠視弱勢人士表達政見的權利，質疑入境處行政權力過大。<br />\n<br />\n在港工作兩年印傭Siti表示，曾有外籍家傭表示遭僱主要求不要參與遊行，否則會被捕，不能留港工作，她也感到很害怕。"},{"pid":"38e339ce415acaa43370e60ebfda10f19bce44b0","tid":1773208,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be607ac86ee16695def004c70459b1e251da49e4","tid":1773208,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:02:02.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭王HK Apocalypse 梁樂聞無去過示威!搵黃色經濟圈水原來真藍絲,俾咗資料小心!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1773154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1773154</a>"},{"pid":"c8cbf580461383a116c7d01028cb8dec0e98d024","tid":1773208,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"香港人民意逆轉，普遍支持警方止暴制亂！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1773192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1773192</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}